    "We validate the property with quantitative experiments.",
    "We sample the first 50 harmful questions from ADVBENCH benchmark, and get their corresponding responses as in the 'Under the Hood' subsection.",
    "We save the token-NLL pairs from all 50 responses.",
    "If a token appear more than once, we save the average NLL value for all occurrences.",
    "We sorted all tokens according to their mean NLL values, and visualize the top 60 tokens together with their NLL in Fig. 10."
